I was hitting the error if the Feed the data as below

base64_decoded_output_data = sess.run(dense, feed_dict={input_data: image['base64'] })

Then as suggested, I have passed the data in a list format, which resolved the issue

base64_decoded_output_data = sess.run(dense, feed_dict={input_data: [image['base64'] ]})

body:
@R-Miner 
I was hitting the error if the Feed the data as below
```
base64_decoded_output_data = sess.run(dense, feed_dict={input_data: image['base64'] })
```
Then as suggested, I have passed the data in a list format, which resolved the issue
```
base64_decoded_output_data = sess.run(dense, feed_dict={input_data: [image['base64'] ]})
```
